== 裁判 ==
[[File:2009_FIFA_Confederations_Cup_ball_by_adidas.JPG|170px]]
國際足協在2009年5月5日公布裁判名單<ref>{{cite news |date=2009-05-05 |title=FIFA appoints match officials |work=FIFA.com |location=[[Zürich|Zürich]] |url=http://www.fifa.com/confederationscup/media/newsid=1054745.html |accessdate=2009-05-26 |archive-date=2009-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090509162716/http://www.fifa.com/confederationscup/media/newsid=1054745.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩個裁判小組（[[危地馬拉|危地馬拉]]的[[Carlos_Batres|Carlos Batres]]和[[巴拉圭|巴拉圭]]的[[Carlos_Amarilla|Carlos Amarilla]]）因傷退出，足協委派[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]的[[阿曼多·阿琛迪亚|阿曼多·阿琛迪亚]]和[[智利|智利]]的[[Pablo_Pozo|Pablo Pozo]]代替<ref>{{cite news |date=2009-06-05 |title=Two referees replaced due to injury |work=FIFA.com |location=[[蘇黎世|蘇黎世]] |url=http://www.fifa.com/confederationscup/media/newsid=1066900.html |accessdate=2009-06-06 |archive-date=2009-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611154151/http://www.fifa.com/confederationscup/media/newsid=1066900.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

